column2: SELECT   s.z,s.velDisp,  s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid,  gl.oiii_#_flux,  gl.oiii_#_flux_err,  gi.bptclass FROM SpecObj AS s  JOIN galSpecIndx AS gi ON s.specObjID = gi.specObjID  JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS sph ON s.specObjID = sph.specObjID  JOIN galSpecLine AS gl ON s.specObjID = gl.specObjID WHERE   s.z BETWEEN # AND #  AND  s.survey = &&&  AND  s.class = &&&  AND  s.snMedian_r > #  AND  s.zWARNING = #
